metadata.name: Leatherfaces #1
metadata.description: Leatherfaces is the first fully licensed PFP (profile picture) project on the Ethereum blockchain. We’re bringing iconic horror franchise, The Texas Chainsaw Massacre to the NFT world in the form of 1666 unique generative NFTs, built from over two hundred and fifty traits and no small amount of love. And the avatars are just the start. They’ll open a door to a variety of member-only perks such as bonus drops, exclusive merch and a darkly wonderful world and community, where we’ll get to play with all kinds of amazing intellectual properties.
